s—alongside its achievements to provide a fully rounded portrait of a vibrant country about to take a commanding position on the world stage.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 24. Mai 2022) 0aSocial changezBrazilxHistoryy21st century. 7aHISTORY / Latin America / South America.2bisacsh08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertYale University Press Complete eBook-Package 2014-2015z978311067250340uhttps://doi.org/10.12987/978030016583840uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9780300165838423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9780300165838/original  a978-3-11-067250-3  Yale University Press Complete eBook-Package 2014-2015c2014d2015  aEBA_FAO  aEBA_UCA_YUP  aGBV-deGruyter-alles